<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Deletion Request Received</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Account Deletion Request Received</h2>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>We have received your request to delete your account. 
        Your request is currently under review and is pending approval by our customer support team.</p>
    <p>Once your request has been reviewed and approved, we will notify you, and the account deletion process will proceed.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or wish to cancel your request, please contact our support team within the next 48 hours.</p>
    <p>Thanks, <br>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
